{"tid":1251583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[逆向思考] 警犬、港共政權,建制派,中共最怕乜?","createTime":"2019-06-22T14:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T15:46:54.000Z","uid":265467,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3018b54fb5d54ce3f8bd22b28c158530fc64f9","tid":1251583,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警犬、港共政權,建制派,中共都係人,係人就一定有弱點,搵出弱點,重拳出擊佢地弱點先會最痛</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">警犬</span></strong><br />\n1. 警犬最怕抗爭者唔犯法,日日比人屌老母鬧狗又無得發洩<br />\n2. 最怕自己內部分化,本身士氣都低,出面比人睇唔起,內部仲要分化埋,士氣更低落<br />\n3. 最怕自己要坐監,哩個唔洗解釋都知點解<br />\n4. 警犬最怕無法提升公信力<br />\n<br />\n警犬依家民望士氣低落,首要希望一定係提升民望同公信力<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">港共政權,建制派,中共</span></strong><br />\n最怕一定唔係香港人同所謂既幾多百萬人遊行,因為現有政制佢地都唔需要負責落台走人,<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">佢地最怕係自身利益同無退路,即係被人抄家產,外國戶照被註銷,生生世世留係大陸,最怕隨時被人清算</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bd8ce3847f5bd32a67e9d2f216a12279dde13b9a","tid":1251583,"uid":245172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:58:25.000Z","msg":"借位一用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YafYzbU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYafYzbU.jpg&h=4522e846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從來冇人當義士係condom<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cRMEcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cRMEcS</a><br />\n<br />\n細心留意其他熱門po<br />\n有部份留言話義士係condom<br />\n驚呢個諗法會潛移默化"},{"pid":"fc7186a14f3cd1f92ebdb704efa6ea32ccb5fe47","tid":1251583,"uid":265643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"最怕冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c72f9f967257569315ea74621de8069e5d3fab0","tid":1251583,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:15:49.000Z","msg":"最怕